case_description: A HubSpot integrated micro-saas solution for Teamwork users. Manage and track client projects from HubSpot.
A HubSpot integrated app that hooks into the major parts of the platform to allow for job and applicant management.
It involved a complete rebrand process, research, website design and development.
Grocom is a free HubSpot CMS theme to create Ecommerce solutions, it is highly focused on Grocery themed stores.
